  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，多点训练总没坏处，对吧？很好。目前还有很多你无法接触到的东西……暂时的。当然你可以主动改变这一点，但凡事都有代价。训练你的技能，然后当你觉得可以时再回来，我就在这静候佳音了。",
    "en": "Alright, more training can't hurt right? Very well then. Theres still a ton of stuff that you don't have access to... Yet. You can change that, but everything comes with a price. Train your skills, then come back if you're feeling like it, I will hear from you."
